        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Mr. Cole moved that the committee rise.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "15:38:50",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on the Crane amendment No. 2, the Chair put the question on agreeing to the amendment and by voice vote, announced the ayes had prevailed. Ms. Lois Frankel (FL) demanded a recorded vote and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "15:25:59",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "DEBATE - Pursuant to the provisions of H. Res. 992, the Committee of the Whole proceeded with 10 minutes of debate on the Crane amendment No. 2.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "15:25:17",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on the Roy amendment No. 1, the Chair put the question on agreeing to the amendment and by voice vote, announced the ayes had prevailed. Mr. Hoyer demanded a recorded vote and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "15:11:53",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "DEBATE - Pursuant to the provisions of H. Res. 992, the Committee of the Whole proceeded with 10 minutes of debate on the Roy amendment No. 1.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:08:36",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "GENERAL DEBATE - The Committee of the Whole proceeded with one hour of general debate on H.R. 7006.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H32400",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:07:33",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "The Speaker designated the Honorable Mike Bost to act as Chairman of the Committee.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H32020",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:07:31",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "House resolved itself into the Committee of the Whole House on the state of the Union pursuant to H. Res. 992 and Rule XVIII.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H8D000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:03:44",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rule provides for consideration of H.R. 7006 with 1 hour of general debate. Motion to recommit allowed. Specified amendments are in order.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H30000",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:03:39",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Considered under the provisions of rule H. Res. 992. (consideration: CR H734-798)",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
        "actionCode": "H1L220",
        "actionDate": "2026-01-14",
        "actionTime": "14:03:25",
        "sourceSystem": {
          "code": 2,
          "name": "House floor actions"
        },
        "text": "Rule H. Res. 992 passed House.",
        "type": "Floor"
      },
      {
